{"tid":535481,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"微信公告：發佈歪曲黨史國史訊息 將被永久封號","createTime":"2018-01-21T02:34:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-21T03:10:24.000Z","uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"b3feb7c68e380f9c0f8882921b6482c070ae3d67","tid":535481,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516497080_ce2f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180121%2Flarge%2F1516497080_ce2f.png&h=96015b98&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n斷章取義、歪曲黨史國史類訊息的例子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180121/large/1516497396_480a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180121%2Flarge%2F1516497396_480a.jpg&h=fe57e394&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n微信18日發表的公告。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n微信公眾平台上周四（18日）發佈公告稱，針對有公眾號、小程序發佈斷章取義、歪曲黨史國史類訊息進行營銷的行為，嚴重者可被永久封號。<br />\n<br />\n公告題為「規範涉黨史國史等訊息發佈行為」，內文指近期微信發現部份公眾號、小程序存在發佈斷章取義、歪曲黨史國史類訊息進行營銷的行為，此類行為已違反《中華人民共和國網絡安全法》、《互聯網用戶公眾賬號管理規定》、《即時通信工具公眾信息服務發展管理暫行規定》、《微信公眾平台運營規範》》、《微信小程序平台運營規範》，涉嫌傳播虛假營銷訊息，對用戶造成騷擾、破壞用戶體驗、擾亂平台的健康生態。<br />\n<br />\n由公告當日起，對於仍存在此類借機營銷行為的公眾號，將對違規文章予以刪除並進行相應處罰，多次處罰後仍繼續違規，或是故意利用各種手段惡意對抗的，將採取更重的處理措施，甚至永久封號。請營運者嚴肅對待不當內容，加強賬號管理，共同維護綠色的網絡環境。<br />\n<br />\n微信團隊在本月10日也發佈了一條公告，打擊發佈低俗、虛假標題和內容的行為。公告稱，對於發送低俗、虛假標題和內容的公眾號，文章進行刪除並實施相應的能力處罰，多次違規處理後仍繼續發送違規內容的，或是故意利用各種手段惡意對抗，將進行永久封號處理。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180121/57734398\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57734398&d=aPFDXfxti3LQ%2Bk6ZABIzW%2F1gJfeR7%2BEkjjir5NquRfg%3D&h=5a7d7794\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180121%2F57734398&h=6d98b5ec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180121/57734398</a>"},{"pid":"892dfd1c8ef0959477316d12afe1c5c7dd38db20","tid":535481,"uid":85819,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:36:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d04f72a954684945fe6aa04d4046c5cf7101aaa7","tid":535481,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:37:09.000Z","msg":"微信雞新玩法"},{"pid":"34c34d6cbb603d44367d8de9072c403bc4a09ef3","tid":535481,"uid":20522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"64算唔算歷史？<br />\n長春圍城算唔算歷史？<br />\n解放軍暗中勾結日軍又算唔算？"},{"pid":"979252aca2b904fbac811c6e59a41f21f1773cd0","tid":535481,"uid":23635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"34c34d6cbb603d44367d8de9072c403bc4a09ef3","tid":535481,"uid":20522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:44:49.000Z","msg":"64算唔算歷史？<br />\n長春圍城算唔算歷史？<br />\n解放軍暗中勾結日軍又算唔算？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:47:09.000Z","msg":"係歪曲嘅黨史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6874267bc7099d0b421b45653a9f93e69225d31f","tid":535481,"uid":51720,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:50:42.000Z","msg":"全宇宙是黨的 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f94029ac84881490fd768b86f1084808cb40682b","tid":535481,"uid":19527,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:56:53.000Z","msg":"大躍進餓死幾千萬人=歪曲黨史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n六四冇死過人=正確黨史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db13741417f3ea8e25206bf2ee2079ac4a97c257","tid":535481,"uid":103127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T02:59:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fea8cbf8e51ec076d4239660dff6fa2254296752","tid":535481,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-21T03:04:27.00